---
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About Me"
	description="A little about Lewis Wang and the interests behind this website."
	pubDate={new Date('July 15 2026')}
>
	<p>
		Hi, I'm Lewis Wang. I usually go by <strong>lewisw</strong> online.
		I'm from China, and Lewis is the English name I use online and in international contexts.
	</p>

	<p>
		I'm not a professional developer. My interest in technology grew through setting up and
		maintaining services for my own use. Along the way, I've learned about domains, email,
		Linux, virtual private servers, networking and self-hosting by working through practical
		problems as they came up.
	</p>

	<p>
		I'm particularly interested in personal domains and email: how a domain represents an
		online identity, how email services differ in practice, and how DNS and mail authentication
		work together. I also enjoy learning more about the infrastructure behind the services I
		use every day.
	</p>

	<p>
		This website is my personal home on the web. For now, it serves as a simple introduction
		and a central place for my links. Over time, I plan to publish occasional notes about things
		I've tried, problems I've solved and decisions I've made. Some posts may be in English and
		others in Chinese.
	</p>

	<p>
		I don't intend to publish on a fixed schedule. I'd rather write when I have an experience
		or idea worth preserving than post simply for the sake of keeping the site active.
	</p>

	<p>
		You can find me on <a href="https://github.com/xaver985">GitHub</a> or contact me at
		<a href="mailto:i@lewisw.net">i@lewisw.net</a>.
	</p>
</Layout>
